<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ shì jī dū yǒng shēng shén de ér zi 迦南810</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì jī dū yǒng shēng shén de ér zi. nǐ shì róng yào
 de jūn wáng, zhǎng quán dào yǒng yuǎn. nǐ shì wǒ de dùn
 pái, míng liàng de chén xīng. wǒ yào zài nǐ de shèng suǒ
 xiàng nǐ jìng bài. bái rì de tài yáng bì bù shāng
 wǒ, yè jiān de yuè liàng bì bù hài wǒ. wǒ chū
 wǒ rù, nǐ dōu bǎo hù wǒ, wǒ zhǔ wǒ shén,
 wǒ yào jìng bài nǐ.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>810</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>